# Convergence wrapper for normal-carryover ISTHMUS sphere ablation.

units si

variable resolution equal 20
variable steps equal 4

voxel material carbon density 1800.0
voxel create solid sphere diameter 1.0e-3 resolution ${resolution} material carbon

source q1 constant 0.8 units kg/m2/s
timestep mass/courant 0.25 source q1

stats 1000000
stats_style step time active-voxels deleted-voxels remaining-mass mass-fraction radius requested-mass-step applied-mass-step dropped-mass-step

variable i loop ${steps}
label ablate-loop
isthmus surface skin voxels solid buffer 1 weighting no map yes
surface flux skin source q1 select all
voxel ablate solid surface skin policy carryover/normal delete yes
run 1
next i
jump SELF ablate-loop

convergence radius exact "initial-radius - q1*time/rho" tolerance 100.0 percent norm final vary resolution 5 10 20 vary steps 1 2 4 order 0.75 2.5 monotonic yes
